{
 "name": "RPlog_Reclaiming_Coruscant",
 "title": "Reclaiming Coruscant",
 "summary": "A massive space battle rages over Coruscant as Imperial and New Republic fleets clash for control of the capital world's skies. Pilots on both sides -- among them the Imperials Alpha-4 (Alex), Aramis, Blake, Keline, and the Republic's Kesander and Vengan in their Ghost-numbered fighters -- duel through the void in a sprawling engagement. The Empire ultimately succeeds in seizing the space over the planet, but the New Republic wins its own quiet victory by successfully evacuating waves of refugees from the area. The log chronicles a hard-fought, costly battle that began when a stray Imperial TIE drifted off patrol and triggered the opening volleys.",
